00:29:18.210 --> 00:29:20.410
know what A is in terms of time.

00:29:20.410 --> 00:29:28.790
And a constant. k1 times A0
e to the minus k1 times time.

00:29:28.790 --> 00:29:30.340
OK, that's my
differential equation

00:29:30.340 --> 00:29:35.370
