B is increasing linearly
in time, at the beginning.

00:39:46.590 --> 00:39:51.190
So B is going up linearly
in time, like this.

00:39:51.190 --> 00:39:55.210
And C is increasing
quadratically in time.

00:39:55.210 --> 00:39:58.120
So it's pretty flat,
